+#   - every DATA-targeting stub's disp32 was rewritten to the correct MOVED pointer target,
+#   - 0 unresolved / 0 unknown / 0 escapes.
+# RED arms: unrewritten-stub cache FAILS; skipped/wrong/corrupt stub FAILS.
